commit.message: Added kind of working server notificaitons.
made the title a link to /
added keywords and some chart resize
Added very basic server notificaiton system.
Fixed a bug where an authorized user would be sent to login page.

Made logging in mandatory.

Fixed most of the firebase errors.

Fixed firebase icons.
notifications can be set from the settings page & are stored in local storage to mak them semi-permanent

Fixed service worker issue.

Fixed issues with --prod build.
Prevented navbar from showing a link ot the current page.
Seperated line and pie chart into components.

Added export capabilites.

You can now export data as CSV or JSON.
